Change Runlevel
  init 0  <-- replace 0 with appropriate runlevel number

RunLevel Configuration file
  /etc/inittab

RunLevels:
  0 - Shut Down
  1 - Single User Mode (no networking)
  2 - Multi User w/no NFS (no networking)
  3 - Multi User Mode (CLI)
  4 - not used/research
  5 - X11 GUI
  6 - reboot
